.curation-data/
# Maintainer curation artifacts (datamodel.md CurationLedger /
# OffensiveQuarantine): they hold player-submitted-but-unaccepted text and
# must never enter this public repo's history. In dev they live under
# .curation-data/ (already ignored above); these named patterns keep them
# out even if CURATION_DATA_PATH points elsewhere — a deliberate belt-and-
# braces redundancy, not an accident.
curation-ledger.json
curation-quarantine.json
curation-snapshot.json
curation-snapshot.summary.txt
curation-events-archive/
.claude/worktrees/

